channel.title: Major Server Error
channel.description:
Hello everyone. I am having a major error with my server. The only people qualified to help me are people that are "Community Members" and/or people I am friends with/I know I can trust. I will offer some sort of a reward(s) depending on how much you help me. -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Problem: I run my private server. Then, when I log in to my server, I log in and then log out about 1 second later. I get the following error in my client: [code]Error: T2 - 53,126,126 - 2488,0,0 - 21,6,3,32,1,114,6,2,-80,5,3,-122,3,5,43,25,1,92,6,1,51,3,1,-49,2,1,-42,9,1,3,11,1,-72,1,1,-84,9,1,31,5,1,-78,1,1,94,23,1,95,23,-1,[/code] This problem is server-wise. In my command prompt, I don't get an error but it appears as if the server is booting everyone without an error making it do so.
Server Base: Pimpscape
(optional) Rating: 10 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Thanks, ~Nets
PS: If I don't answer for some time, or the topic is gone, please add me on MSN and AIM and we will further discuss my problem there. Thank you. ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------[br][size=1]Posted on: December 25, 2006, 10:02:20 AM[/size][hr] Please respond.
